{"id": 82, "genre": 1000, "title": "食物推出迷你装，你怎么看？", "description": "奥利奥推出小饼干，星巴克推出迷你杯咖啡，原本一大块的巧克力变成小包装，方便面也出了小杯装……结果也是不太一样：小饼干没变便宜，迷你杯咖啡还是很大，方便面则变得太小，一口就吃完了……\r\n", "record_count": 1581, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194401D9E6hlraz2m4wHtC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-09-24T07:58:54Z", "questions": [{"id": 90, "title": "食物推出迷你装，你怎么看？", "content": "食物推出迷你装，你怎么看？\r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 779, "content": "我喜欢小包装，一个人大包吃不完", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193127H5vEUbgpGTwVJtzM.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 780, "content": "我喜欢小包装，因为可以给小朋友吃", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161821romxfQES2ua7hRg8.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 781, "content": "我不喜欢小包装，商家不就是为了缺斤少两吗", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161821D9UH7npacCKfdBZw.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 782, "content": "我不喜欢小包装，吃一个拆一个费劲", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161822TJDdbqUK4oE1MFtH.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 783, "content": "我不喜欢这些新概念新营销什么的", "image": "img/option/option/201606061618227fXCRskFp0jYJmUq.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 784, "content": "啊？我根本没注意到还有小包装啊！", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161822FDqskrtKjM246dcQ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}